# MacOS X Button Setup
# Written by Maciej Delmanowski <harnir@linux.net.pl>
#
# This is the window titlebar button setup similar to the MacOS X
# buttons on the titlebar

# First button - close
Mouse 3 1 N Close
Mouse 1 1 M Kill
Mouse 2 1 N Nop
Style * Button 1

Style * NoButton 2

# Second button - iconify
Mouse 3 3 N Iconify
Mouse 1 3 N Nop
Mouse 2 3 N Nop
Style * Button 3

Style * NoButton 4

# third button - various ways to maximize a window
Mouse 3 5 N Maximize 90 88
Mouse 2 5 N Maximize 0 100
Mouse 1 5 N Maximize 
Style * Button 5

Style * NoButton 6

Style * NoButton 7

Style * NoButton 8

Style * NoButton 9

Style * NoButton 0

# vim:ft=fvwm
